You have exceeded your premium request allowance. We have automatically switched you to GPT-4.1 which is included with your plan. [Enable additional paid premium requests](command:chat.enablePremiumOverages) to continue using premium models.```seqdiag
actor User
boundary ProductDetailPage
control ProductController
participant ":ProductService" as Service
participant ":ProductModel" as Model
database Database

User->ProductDetailPage: 1. Open product detail page
activate ProductDetailPage
activate User

ProductDetailPage->ProductController: 2. GET /products/{id}
activate ProductController

ProductController->Service: 5. Process product detail retrieval
activate Service

alt Product not found
    Service->Model: 6.1 Find product by ID
    activate Model
    Model->Database: 6.1.1 Retrieve product data by ID
    activate Database
    Database-->Model: 6.1.2 Result (null)
    deactivate Database
    Model-->Service: 6.1.3 Return not found
    deactivate Model
    Service-->ProductController: 6.1.4 Return not found result
    ProductController-->ProductDetailPage: 6.1.5 Return 404 Not Found + message
    ProductDetailPage-->User: 6.1.6 Show "Product not found"
else Product found
    Service->Model: 6.2 Find product by ID
    activate Model
    Model->Database: 6.2.1 Retrieve product data by ID
    activate Database
    Database-->Model: 6.2.2 Product data
    deactivate Database
    Model-->Service: 6.2.3 Return product entity
    deactivate Model
    Service-->ProductController: 6.2.4 Return ProductDetailResponse
    deactivate Service
    ProductController-->ProductDetailPage: 6.2.5 Return 200 OK + product data
    deactivate ProductController
end

ProductDetailPage-->User: 7. Display detail page content
deactivate ProductDetailPage
deactivate User
